  "title": "幼儿园华文老师",
  "description": "<p><strong>Requirements 要求</strong><br />1. 华文母语水平<br />2. 对于<strong>0-3岁</strong>幼儿教育及蒙特梭利教育抱有热忱<br />3. 必须持有ECDA认证的 <strong>EY2C </strong>或 <strong>EY2 </strong>或 <strong>L1</strong><br />4. 刚修读完ACEY还未被正式认证者，同样欢迎申请<br />5. 在读ACEY，准备毕业者，同样欢迎申请</p><p><u><em><strong>请注意：只招聘全职老师</strong></em></u></p><p><strong>工作地址：</strong>963C Upper Changi Rd N, #02-01 to 06, Singapore 506790 (Komo Shoppes Level 2) 提交申请前，请先查询工作地点是否适合<br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities 职责</strong><br />1. Plan and deliver lessons in line with the school’s curriculum and teaching philosophy<br />2. Maintain children's observation records and their progress reports <br />3. Prepare children's portfolios for PTC sessions in accordance with the school's PTC schedules<br />4. Establish and maintain good communications and relationships with parents<br />5. Be responsible for children's general well-being in areas concerning social behaviour, safety and hygiene<br />6. Work closely with parents, colleagues, and management to maintain a high standard of childcare service</p><p></p><p></p>",
